OL,7,FThe family of an accountant who died
OL,8,Fafter he was attacked outside a
OL,9,Fnightclub in Brighton, 25 years ago,
OL,10,Fare calling for a full public inquiry
OL,11,Finto the case.
OL,13,FJay Abatan, a father-of-two from
OL,14,FWorthing, was fatally injured in
OL,15,FJanuary 1999. He died five days later.
OL,16,FHis brother believes the attack was
OL,17,Fracially-motivated.
