OL,7,FSussex Police were heavily criticised
OL,8,Fover their handling of the
OL,9,Finvestigation, and no-one has ever
OL,10,Fbeen convicted.
OL,12,FCampaigners gathered outside Brighton
OL,13,FPolice Station yesterday (Sunday 28
OL,14,FJanuary) calling for justice.
OL,16,FJay's brother, Michael, was also
OL,17,Ftargeted in the same incident, outside
OL,18,Fthe Ocean Rooms in Morley Street.
