OL,7,FAt an inquest into his death in 2010,
OL,8,Fa coroner recorded a verdict of
OL,9,Funlawful killing.
OL,11,FIn 2020, Sussex Police offered a
OL,12,F#10,000 reward for new leads.
OL,14,FDespite the incident being
OL,15,Finvestigated, no one was ever brought
OL,16,Fto trial.
