OL,7,FA Sussex Police spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Jay Abatan was assaulted 25 years ago
OL,9,Fduring a night out in Brighton on 24
OL,10,FJanuary 1999, and tragically died as a
OL,11,Fresult of the head injury he sustained
OL,12,Ffive days later.
OL,14,F"Two men were arrested and charged in
OL,15,Fconnection with his death, but were
OL,16,Flater cleared of lesser charges of
OL,17,Faffray and assault following a trial.
