OL,7,F"In 2020, we repeated our appeal for
OL,8,Finformation about this tragic death
OL,9,Fand offered a #10,000 reward for any
OL,10,Finformation leading to the arrest and
OL,11,Fconviction of any person responsible
OL,12,Ffor the death of Jay. A potential
OL,13,Fwitness came forward however there was
OL,14,Fno information from this witness which
OL,15,Fcould assist the investigation and
OL,16,Fthere are currently no developments in
OL,17,Fthe case.J"We remain committed to
OL,18,Finvestigating any new information that
OL,19,Fwill assist in convicting those
OL,20,Fresponsible for the death of Jay."
